{"tid":2504943,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔計政治，中國歷史科確實係一本好好睇嘅故事書嚟","createTime":"2021-04-26T08:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T15:39:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e85817500362d5fcaa1183fabf716e80b7dffb63","tid":2504943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:54:40.000Z","msg":"講到做漢人係好光榮嘅事，講到中原地大物博係因為個個外族都爭住做漢人，覺得做漢人好威所以自動將自己國家土地送畀漢人咁，所以中原地大物博唔係因為侵略，而係啲人自願畀嘅，因為做漢人好威"},{"pid":"f1a931de6d3e3cc0748e10d1936263ae9fdadd3a","tid":2504943,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"大漢沙文主義？"},{"pid":"5b8d45b2f88527744ade72474f6a049316f1be5a","tid":2504943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1a931de6d3e3cc0748e10d1936263ae9fdadd3a","tid":2504943,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"大漢沙文主義？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:33:59.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"4dac001993063d6a67214ecaff7dc4ceec521697","tid":2504943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6027e06631f7154851c98bd199ba7c1251566eb","tid":2504943,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1a931de6d3e3cc0748e10d1936263ae9fdadd3a","tid":2504943,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"大漢沙文主義？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"中國人視角自HIGH<br />\n<br />\n香港的中史教科書，過去一直係以中華民國（國民黨）視角編寫，未來會以中華人民共和國（共產黨）視角編寫。"},{"pid":"01325a84196b3e5c3352377bde239255af6bb06e","tid":2504943,"uid":346584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"中共式歷史<br />\n點解八國洋蠻唔將土地交給本朝大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a14ab0dd97dce86fe761b4f806bca8f4859d743","tid":2504943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dis